<p><strong>宋飞<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-3" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-3')">3</a></sup>电影宇宙奖：</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2038009); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2038009&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609905444" alt="TyGently" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2038009)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2038009); return false;">TyGently</a></span>，相应作品<a class="newpage" href="/clash-of-the-cosmic-comedians">Clash of the Cosmic Comedians</a>。理由：构建了“杰瑞·宋飞拯救世界”故事系列。</p>
<p><strong>西西里加奖<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-4" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-4')">4</a></sup>：</strong> 仍然是 <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2038009); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2038009&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609905444" alt="TyGently" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2038009)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2038009); return false;">TyGently</a></span>，相应作品<a class="newpage" href="/clash-of-the-cosmic-comedians">Clash of the Cosmic Comedians</a>。理由：把三个主题完美融合到了同一个故事中（即使是分了三部分的故事）。</p>
<p><strong>斯特凡松奖<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-5" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-5')">5</a></sup>：</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3009022); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3009022&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609905444" alt="not_a_seagull" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3009022)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3009022); return false;">not_a_seagull</a></span>，相应作品<a href="/not-a-seagull-proposal">not_a_seagull的提案</a>。理由：有勇气去完成一份001提案。</p>
<p><strong>“我父亲的价值观”奖：</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gekkoguy" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2923244); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2923244&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609905444" alt="Gekkoguy" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2923244)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gekkoguy" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2923244); return false;">Gekkoguy</a></span>。理由：所有作品的题目都出自同一首歌的歌词，即Jethro Tull的《Thick as a Brick》。</p>
